latestPosts.caption: It’s my favorite time of the year, how could I not do a little Secret Santa with my team 🥰♥️🎄

Have been a fan of Sephora since eons! It’s always been the place I spent the most amount of time and money at 😋 Safe to say I have multiple favorite products from there, here are some of my go-to this wedding season: 

- @hudabeauty Easy Blur Primer & Foundation

- @rarebeauty Blush & Highlighter

- @benefitindia Brow Mascara & Benetint

- @smashboxindia Eyeshadow Palette

- @toofaced Better Than Sex Mascara

Tried and loved every time!

Transforming beauty for a day as magical as love itself ♥️✨
